  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Improved empirical parametrizations of the γ ⁎ N → N (1535) transition amplitudes and the Siegert's theorem</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="260" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
